    "abstract": "<jats:title>ABSTRACT</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We studied 2780 adults in Hong Kong who received CoronaVac inactivated virus vaccine (Sinovac) and BNT162b2 mRNA vaccine (\u201cComirnaty\u201d, BioNTech/Fosun Pharma). We found stronger and more durable antibody responses to two doses of the mRNA vaccine, and slightly stronger initial antibody responses to each vaccine in younger adults and women.</jats:p>",
